<plot>A sophmoric, heartfelt comedy about misconceptions of meaningful relationships. Kaleo Smith is a confused twenty-something who is unsure of what he wants, especially when it comes to women. He thinks it's sex, as reinforced by his best friend Kyle, and never thought it might be his best friend, Adriana, who's always by his side. As Kyle wises up and tells Kaleo that sex isn't everything, it might be too late, as Adriana may have moved on.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?245414</url></doc>
